comments: Wickham is just a great guy. He is a nice and easy going professor. Usually weekly assignments that are about 12 a page to 1 page long. A lot of reading in front of the class but it\'s not presentation format just sitting there and reading what you wrote for 30 seconds. This is a great opportunity to get creative with every single assignment.

comments: Wickham is one of the best professors at SUCO. Great guy, super nice, hilarious... just a good guy... Looked forward to class every day. Yes it\'s an easy A, but don\'t take advantage of him... he\'s a good guy! Projects were easy and enjoyable. Tom Clack was great too. Lots of great stories. I recommend this class and this professor.
